            <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 11:33:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Remio Host 1.8.2 &mdash; keeps getting smoother</h2>
                <p>A big reliability release.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Rock-solid connections</strong> &mdash; connecting and reconnecting is faster and far steadier, with much more reliable session recovery.</li>
                    <li><strong>No more reconnect flash</strong> &mdash; fixed the brief black screen that could appear on a quick reconnect.</li>
                    <li><strong>Cursor appears instantly</strong> &mdash; your mouse pointer shows up the moment a session starts.</li>
                    <li><strong>Sharper device preview</strong> &mdash; the screenshot of your PC in the device list stays crisp instead of occasionally going black.</li>
                    <li><strong>Cleaner taskbar &amp; tray icon</strong> &mdash; a crisp, logo-only icon.</li>
