        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1.0</title>
            <sparkle:version>1.1.0</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>10.0.17763</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 07:55:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Your PC, anywhere. Now smoother than ever.</h2>
                <p>Remio Host 1.1.0 is our biggest Windows update yet &mdash; faster connections, calmer streams, and a streaming engine you can finally <em>feel</em>.</p>
                <h3>What's new</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>A stream that just flows</strong> &mdash; smoother frame pacing, fewer hiccups when the network blips, and a renderer that gracefully recovers from latency spikes.</li>
                    <li><strong>One-click pairing</strong> &mdash; tightened signaling handshake, smarter reconnect, and a UI that stays in sync even when Wi-Fi drops.</li>
                    <li><strong>Type, click, command</strong> &mdash; new TextField focus monitor makes your iPad keyboard and trackpad feel native.</li>
                    <li><strong>Drag-and-drop file transfer</strong> &mdash; finally first-class on the Windows host.</li>
                    <li><strong>Built like a service</strong> &mdash; runs as a true Windows Service, survives reboots, log-outs, and user switching.</li>
                    <li><strong>Calmer diagnostics</strong> &mdash; rebuilt streaming logger, easier to read, easier to debug.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Plus countless little fixes nobody asked for, but everybody wanted. Update now and feel the difference.</p>
            ]]></description>
